{"tid":440522,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過啲post係你覺得膠得黎你係笑左","createTime":"2017-10-19T00:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T10:47:42.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c555ba1a132e158a3fbe5d55d5e52f6a5bcfc4b0","tid":440522,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:38:28.000Z","msg":"但頭幾個回覆就比啲懶係野既人打句幽默感乜乜乜既reply破壞左，之後成班人on99就跟風走去恥笑接龍咁樣，搞到你都即刻無晒mood撳上一頁出返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8c26d3286ff159edac4cfb050106e70309a103","tid":440522,"uid":139676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:42:14.000Z","msg":"up乜9"},{"pid":"52c29386ac4190e1a5e5d3bc72eec3dcdba00a17","tid":440522,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>up乜9</blockquote><br />\n即係有啲搞笑post你本身覺得幾好笑<br />\n但係頭幾個reply就有啲懶醒既人回埋啲<br />\n幽默感既野點點點 果啲reply<br />\n跟住果啲回覆通常就會一面倒恥笑樓主戇鳩又盛，破壞晒人地個post<br />\n搞到你都唔想再理出返去"},{"pid":"f4a7e8bf4205f9db08126b6e69f110831e23dbb4","tid":440522,"uid":14476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:49:01.000Z","msg":"巴打 我留意左你好耐<br />\n你真係好幽默<br />\n<br />\n我自問都算個ok幽默既人 但係你幽默感比我真係高十幾二十倍<br />\n<br />\n錯 應該係100倍先岩<br />\n<br />\n估唔到我係呢個post竟然見識到你既威力<br />\n<br />\n我真係笑到爆左肚 依家一路打字一路撿返d腸呀內臟呀腎呀<br />\n<br />\n塞返落個肚到<br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過未來幾個月去紅館開棟篤笑?"},{"pid":"a78bb1beb672e48d8b1d9c3e5d689642b0a7580a","tid":440522,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"無人回？<br />\n係既，連登仔就係做開呢啲野，點會敢面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9aa7f80837a7afab033820da3b49139394d3